Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難不成— 是我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該怎麼辦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別想了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別再深究這事了 霧島海人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天那樣才不是對學姐告白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就像前天那樣 學姐不是也沒反應過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放平常心哦 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可比海人年長 不振作怎麼能行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像平常那樣做好早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後稍微努力一下 試著做個便當
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是和學姐同住在這屋簷下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要保持平常心哦 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}平常至終 和往常一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}平常心 平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想做就能做到的 要有自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…這麼說有點怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不如說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:02:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}NO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}天…天氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天看來會放晴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}馬上就要…期末考了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我讀書不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上吃了啥我都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這麼早起真是難得一見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偶…偶爾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和你走散了…然後也沒去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說回來 都是檸檬學姐和美櫻不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天我誠懇道歉了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 聽我說啊 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天不單是檸檬學姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗和美櫻也去偷窺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 霧島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}發生什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你說「什麼」是想指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為你態度和平常不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎…沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我超正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天…你去輕井澤了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去買東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在輕井澤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然是…讓她困擾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會…沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是因為突然了點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以內心有些動搖了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我其實也…對海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好~兩情相悅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不喜歡搞基
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是我的反應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}便當？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才一夏學姐拜託我給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說「幫我拿給小海」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐她？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}人家難得給你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個啊…哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我只是在假設啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}A雄君向B子醬說了像是告白的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 B子醬一言不發的回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再然後B子醬對A雄君的態度就變得有些不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請問B子醬的心理狀態是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在困擾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}A美醬聽到B太君說了像是告白的話後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}由於太過驚訝就從那裡逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡問題來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請問A美醬應該採取什麼態度？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應該做個答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}順便問一下 A美醬覺得B太君怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定不是討厭他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}甚至覺得他有點可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就答應咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這問題…才沒有這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是因為…A美醬她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會離開這個小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}B子醬確實覺得很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過無法確定她是覺得很煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還是需要些時間來考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得A雄君還是不要急於得到答覆來得好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要急…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在偷懶 被我發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了？累了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個啊…早上忘了問你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天我們走散之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你去幹嘛了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也沒辦法 只好回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你有找我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎呀 這不是霧島同學和谷川同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼啊…原來是檸檬學姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這招呼真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明看到魅力十足的年長女性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正展現著妖艷的泳裝姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「妖艷」什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只不過是學校泳衣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要集合咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我們走吧 檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}A美醬似乎有個叫C子醬的情敵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道說 你還在和貴月學姐鬧彆扭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你得振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然說 因為貴月學姐是外國人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在交流方面可能會有許多問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐孤身一人來到這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或許正感到不安啊…寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在這方面海人應該多關照她一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…嗯 說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 正如谷川所說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我只顧著想自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 我覺得肯為他人著想的海人很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 C子醬在猛踩地雷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}C子醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我得振作一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}振作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什…什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}關於昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我作出了奇怪的反應真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 我沒有那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 我們回歸往常那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回歸往常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就用這招打破現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我要做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不做不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想做！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼慾求不滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 那是當然！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真 真奈美姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那要我來和你做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什 麼 都 可 以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搞不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}裝什麼純呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}阿海 我正要去購物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反對無效 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真是明鑒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學你這份心意讓我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 我們才相識不久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 能不能給我一點時間再作答覆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會在好好考慮過海人的各方面後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好好的做出答覆的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那之前 讓我們像往常一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會聽從學姐的意見的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就這麼跟他說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那位女性是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…這到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天才向我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然我沒有好好答覆他也有不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒過一天 竟然就和別的女人約會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難以置信！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:12:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}煩惱著的我簡直就像笨蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 隨他的便了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}用連環讓我進行跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(524,664)}linkage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這次再不回應我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}後果很嚴重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音 這是因為 那個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐拜託了我要照顧海人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被｢拜託了」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}僅此而已 僅此而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個和這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要買這麼多嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這次是長期戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 接著要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…真奈美姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明就心裡偷著樂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才沒那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}竟 竟然那麼大膽！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}阿海 想看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼樣 好看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…哦…呃 完美到極致了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以快點買了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人 到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如何 我比那個叫一夏的女生要好多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那種告白了也不答覆的女生 還是忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我先去洗個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你隨便喝個茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要一起洗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打從心底拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去之後得和學姐說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學…學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這種小事無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別問了 先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就這麼想待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 應該先打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼我會這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幹什麼吵吵鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這女生是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道是阿海的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是受他姐姐之託來照顧海人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海拜託的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以不能讓海人留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼 不是戀愛自由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你看起來比他可大上不少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}年齡不是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人還是高中生呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛總是伴隨著阻礙的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真奈美姐你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你還不懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是電燈泡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我有保護海人的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}僅僅如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}僅僅是這樣的理由就讓你擅自闖進別人家裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太不合理了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}差不多該從實招來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你來這裡真正的目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才沒什麼真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}阿海 這孩子真是相當遲鈍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:16:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 算了隨便你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這也是年輕人的樂子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你怎麼又來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐…姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 海 連一夏學姐都來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是姐姐帶來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那隨便坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 你別穿成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去換衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同學 那個…你說「姐姐」是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還沒介紹過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是我姐姐小倉真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小倉…可姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.97,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}在日本結婚後婦隨夫姓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐她一和老公吵架就跑回來發牢騷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這次絕饒不了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼吵架？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那傢伙擅自就把我錄的節目刪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無聊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可是很期待的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了好了 快回智叔那裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算他下跪也不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原諒他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這回真是受夠他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你到底是幫誰的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說回來 我才是讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總的來說還是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事 都怪真奈美姐說了些讓人誤解的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會那樣也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓我賠禮補償你吧 幹什麽都行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼都行？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個時候 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實是很想問的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請告訴我昨天的答覆 我在你心裡是什麼地位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:19:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我讀書不太好 學姐…能教教我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我盡量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那裡拼寫錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那裡不是“E”而是“I”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}英語做完了以後是數學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 該睡覺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天還要上學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}離期末考試沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}照你這成績 你姐姐會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至少要考到平均分以上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要及格就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你首先態度就不端正
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是你叫我教你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來 做題目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是沒說就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:54.60,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}這裡他說的是前輩（せんぱい）的後半部分和おっぱい 胸部的尾音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的姐啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 胸部？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒想到學姐還有那種性格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人 學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 現在是午休啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}邊吃邊學啊 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 好辛苦的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 但是挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人和貴月學姐不再鬧彆扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 C子醬真遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你幹什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 別隨便摸女孩子的頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦~女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 你再說一遍試試！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暑假將始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}縱使一生也不會忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難忘的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想這…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對大家來說也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論是歡喜抑或是悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}概其總總
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一生只此一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}彼夏伊始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an1}我識破了一夏學姐的真實身份了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an1}別說出來 不然我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an1}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an1}哲郎死翹翹了

